<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-09-0394 </DOCNO><TEXT>A reclamation method called Biological Reclamation Process (BRP), developedin Europe, requiring no topsoil storage, handling and redistribution,has proven that successful reclamation of surface mined land can be accomplishedwhereby ecological balance and fertility will be restored within oneyear after mining. The purpose of this paper is to discuss the feasibilityof the application of BRP in the United States of America.</TEXT></DOC>